WEBVTT

00:00:56.997 --> 00:01:01.153
And for this service, they were murdered,

00:01:01.153 --> 00:01:03.615
their families torn apart,

00:01:03.615 --> 00:01:05.817
and their story largely forgotten.

00:01:06.827 --> 00:01:09.974
No one was ever sentenced
for these crimes.

00:01:10.884 --> 00:01:13.041
I cannot forget them.

00:01:13.041 --> 00:01:15.090
They live in me somehow,

00:01:15.090 --> 00:01:18.320
their memories giving me
meaning every day.

00:01:18.320 --> 00:01:22.751
But they are also haunting
the dark street of my mind.

00:01:22.751 --> 00:01:24.712
As humanitarian aid workers,

00:01:24.712 --> 00:01:28.064
they made the choice
to be at the side of the victim,

00:01:28.064 --> 00:01:32.661
to provide some assistance,
some comfort, some protection,